    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='221:248'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-1a' );" name="018-1a" class="pb">[018-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='248:261'>禮記要義卷第十九　樂記</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='261:271'>　一樂記分合源流</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='271:291'>案鄭目録云名曰樂記者以其記樂之義此於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='291:311'>別録屬樂記蓋十一篇合爲一篇謂有樂本有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='311:331'>樂論有樂施有樂言有樂禮有樂情有樂化有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='331:351'>樂象有賔牟賈有師乙有魏文侯今雖合此略</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='351:371'>有分焉案藝文志云黃帝以下至三代各有當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='371:391'>代之樂名孔子曰移風易俗莫善於樂周衰禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='391:411'>壞其樂尤微以音律爲節又爲鄭衛所亂故無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='411:438'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-1b' );" name="018-1b" class="pb">[018-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='438:458'>遺法矣漢興制氏以雅樂聲律丗爲樂官頗能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='458:478'>記其鏗鎗皷舞而巳不能言其義理武帝時河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='478:498'>間獻王始博古與生等共采周官及諸子云樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='498:518'>事者以作樂記事也其内史丞王度傳之以授</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='518:538'>常山王禹成帝時爲謁者數言其義献二十四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='538:558'>卷樂記劉向校書得樂記二十三篇與禹不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='558:578'>其道浸以益微故劉向所校二十三篇著於别</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='578:598'>録今樂記所斷取十一篇餘有十二篇其名猶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='598:610'>在二十四卷記無所録也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='610:637'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-2a' );" name="018-2a" class="pb">[018-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='637:649'>　二聲音變方樂舞之別</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='649:669'>凡音之起由人心生也人心之動物使之然也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='669:689'>感於物而動故形於聲聲相應故生變變成方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='689:709'>謂之音比音而樂之及干戚羽旄謂之樂樂者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='709:729'>音之所由生也其本在人心之感於物也注云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='729:749'>宫啇角徴羽雜比曰音單岀曰聲形猶見也樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='749:769'>之器彈其宫則衆宫應然不足樂是以變之使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='769:789'>雜也易曰同聲相應同氣相求春秋傳曰若以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='789:809'>水濟水誰能食之若琴瑟之專一誰能聽之方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='809:836'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-2b' );" name="018-2b" class="pb">[018-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='836:856'>猶文章也干盾也戚斧也武舞所執也羽翟羽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='856:876'>也旄旄牛尾也文舞所執周禮舞師樂師掌教</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='876:896'>舞有兵舞有干舞有羽舞有旄舞詩曰左手執</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='896:903'>籥右手秉翟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='903:914'>三朱弦䟽越大羮元酒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='914:934'>清廟之瑟朱弦而䟽越壹倡而三歎有遺音者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='934:954'>矣大饗之禮尚玄酒而爼腥魚大羮不和有遺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='954:974'>味者矣注云清廟謂作樂歌清廟也朱絃練朱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='974:994'>絃練則聲濁越瑟厎孔也畫䟽之使聲逹也倡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='994:1021'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-3a' );" name="018-3a" class="pb">[018-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1021:1041'>發歌句也三歎三人從歎之耳大饗祫祭先王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1041:1061'>以腥魚爲爼實不臑孰之大羮肉湆不調以鹽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1061:1068'>菜遺猶餘也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1068:1082'>四哀樂喜怒敬愛之感非性也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1082:1102'>六者非性也感於物而后動者結外感物也人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1102:1122'>生而静天之性也性本静寂無此六事六事之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1122:1142'>生由應感外物而動故云非性也所以知非性</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1142:1162'>者今設取一人以此六事觸之言此人必隨觸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1162:1182'>而動故知非本性也庾云隨其所感而應之是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1182:1209'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-3b' );" name="018-3b" class="pb">[018-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1209:1229'>知非性也此聲皆據人心感於物而口爲聲知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1229:1245'>是人聲也故鄭注云言人聲在所見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1245:1257'>　五五音爲君臣民事物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1257:1277'>宫爲君者宫則主君所以然者鄭注月令云宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1277:1297'>屬土土居中央揔四方君之象也又土爰稼穡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1297:1317'>猶君能滋生萬民也又五音以絲多聲重者爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1317:1337'>尊宫絃最大用八十一絲故宫爲君崔氏云五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1337:1357'>音之次以宫最濁自宫以下則稍清矣君臣民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1357:1378'>事物亦有尊卑故以次配之　啇爲臣者啇所以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1378:1405'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-4a' );" name="018-4a" class="pb">[018-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1405:1425'>爲臣者何以鄭注月令云啇屬金以其濁次宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1425:1445'>臣之象也解者云宫八十一絲啇七十二絲次</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1445:1465'>宫如臣之得次君之貴重也崔氏云啇是金金</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1465:1484'>以决斷爲義臣事君亦以義斷爲賢矣角爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1484:1504'>民所以爲民者鄭注月令云角屬木以其清濁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1504:1524'>中民之象也解者云宫濁而羽清角六十四絲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1524:1544'>聲居宫羽之中半清半濁故云以其清濁中也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1544:1564'>民比君臣爲劣比事物爲優故云角清濁中民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1564:1584'>之象矣崔氏云角屬春春時物生衆皆有區別</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1584:1611'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-4b' );" name="018-4b" class="pb">[018-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1611:1631'>亦象萬民衆多而有區別也　徴爲事所以爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1631:1651'>事者鄭注月令云徴屬火以其徴清事之象也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1651:1671'>解者云羽最清徴次之故用五十四絲是徴清</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1671:1691'>徴清所以爲事之象也夫事是造爲造爲由民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1691:1711'>故先事後乃有物也是事勝於物而劣於民故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1711:1731'>次民居物之前所以徴爲事之象也崔氏云徴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1731:1751'>屬夏夏時生長萬物皆成形體事亦有體故以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1751:1771'>徴配事也　羽爲物羽所以爲物者鄭注月令</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1771:1791'>云羽屬水者以其最清物之象也解云羽者最</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1791:1818'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-5a' );" name="018-5a" class="pb">[018-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1818:1838'>清用四十八絲而爲物劣於事故最處末所以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1838:1858'>羽爲物也崔氏云羽屬冬冬物聚則成財用冬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1858:1878'>則物皆藏聚與財相類也　五音不亂則無怗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1878:1898'>懘之音矣者怗敝也懘敗也敝敗謂不和之貌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1898:1918'>也若君臣民事物五者各得其所用不相壞亂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1918:1938'>則五音之響無敝敗矣　宫亂則荒其君驕者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1938:1958'>前明音聲與政通若五事皆正則音不敝敗是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1958:1978'>聲與政通故此以下明聲與政通也若五音之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1978:1998'>敝敗則政亂各有所由也荒猶散也若宫音之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1998:2025'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-5b' );" name="018-5b" class="pb">[018-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2025:2045'>亂則其聲放散是知由其君驕溢故也崔氏云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2045:2065'>宫聲所以散者由君驕也若君驕則萬物荒散</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2065:2085'>也　啇亂則陂其官壞者陂不平正也若啇音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2085:2105'>之亂則其聲欹邪而不正也是知由其臣不治</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2105:2125'>於官官壞故也崔氏云啇聲所以傾邪者由臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2125:2143'>官壞也官若壞則物皆傾邪也<span class='krp-note'>云云</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2143:2157'>　六五音之義之聲之和之動</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2157:2177'>案樂緯動聲儀云宫爲君君者當寛大容衆故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2177:2196'>聲弘以舒其和情以柔動脾也啇爲臣臣者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2196:2223'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-6a' );" name="018-6a" class="pb">[018-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2223:2243'>以發明君之號令其聲散以明其和温以斷動</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2243:2263'>肺也角爲民民者當約儉不奢僣差故其聲防</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2263:2283'>以約其和清以静動肝也徴爲事事者君子之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2283:2303'>功旣當急就之其事當乆流亡故其聲貶以疾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2303:2323'>其和平以功動心也羽爲物物者不有委聚故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2323:2343'>其聲散以虚其和斷以散動腎也動聲儀又云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2343:2363'>若宫唱而啇和是謂善大平之樂注云君臣相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2363:2383'>和又云角從宫是謂哀衰國之樂注云象人有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2383:2403'>怨訴又云羽從宫徃而不反是謂悲亡國之樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2403:2430'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-6b' );" name="018-6b" class="pb">[018-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2430:2433'>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2433:2442'>七朱弦䟽越三歎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2442:2462'>正義曰朱弦練朱弦者案虞書傳云古者帝王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2462:2482'>升歌清廟之樂大琴練絃此云朱絃者明練之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2482:2502'>可知也云練則聲濁者不練則體勁而聲清練</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2502:2522'>則絲孰而絃濁云越瑟厎孔畫䟽之使聲遲也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2522:2542'>者熊氏云瑟兩頭有孔畫䟽之䟽通也使兩頭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2542:2562'>孔相連而通孔小則聲急孔大則聲遲故云使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2562:2582'>聲遲也云三歎三人從歎之耳者三歎謂擊瑟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2582:2609'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-7a' );" name="018-7a" class="pb">[018-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2609:2627'>賛歎美者但有三人歎之耳言歎者少也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2627:2634'>八性情之別</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2634:2655'>正義曰言人𥘉生未有情欲是其静稟於自然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2655:2675'>是天性也　感於物而動性之欲也者其心本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2675:2695'>雖静感於外物而心遂動是性之所貪欲也自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2695:2711'>然謂之性貪欲謂之情是情性別也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2711:2730'>九鄭氏以聖賢精氣爲神鬼䟽謂鬼神有三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2730:2750'>大樂與天地同和大禮與天地同節和故百物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2750:2770'>不失節故祀天祭地明則有禮樂幽則有鬼神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2770:2797'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-7b' );" name="018-7b" class="pb">[018-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2797:2817'>注云言順天地之氣與其數不失其性成物有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2817:2837'>功報焉教人者助天地成物者也易曰是故知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2837:2857'>鬼神之情狀與天地相似五帝德說黃帝德也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2857:2877'>死而民畏其神者百年春秋傳曰若敖氏之鬼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2877:2897'>然則聖人之精氣謂之神賢知之精氣謂之鬼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2897:2917'>正義曰天地與隂陽生養爲氣樂有六律六吕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2917:2937'>調和生養是順天地之氣解經同和也云與其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2937:2957'>數謂天有日月星辰地有山川髙下其數不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2957:2977'>故云與其數解經同節也易上繫辭云精氣爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2977:3004'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-8a' );" name="018-8a" class="pb">[018-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3004:3024'>物遊魂爲變是故知鬼神之情狀與天地相似</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3024:3044'>注云精氣謂七八遊魂謂九六遊魂謂之鬼物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3044:3064'>終所歸精氣謂之神物生所信也言木火之神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3064:3084'>生物東南金水之鬼終物西北二者之情其狀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3084:3104'>與春夏生物秋冬終物相似云五帝德說黃帝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3104:3124'>德曰死而民畏其神者百年案大戴禮五帝德</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3124:3143'>篇云春秋傳曰若敖氏之鬼引春秋者宣四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3143:3163'>年左傳又鄭注祭法七祀謂鬼神司察小過引</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3163:3183'>此幽則有鬼神然則有天地自然之鬼神有聖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3183:3210'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-8b' );" name="018-8b" class="pb">[018-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3210:3224'>人賢人之鬼神有七祀之鬼神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3224:3234'>　十舞行綴逺與短</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3234:3254'>其治民勞者其舞行綴逺其治民逸者其舞行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3254:3274'>綴短注云民勞則德薄相去逺舞人少也民逸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3274:3294'>則德盛鄼相去近舞人多也正義曰鄼謂鄼聚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3294:3308'>舞人行位之處立表鄼以識之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3308:3325'><span class='krp-note'>十/一</span>樂感人深本從民心而來</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3325:3345'>其感人深者言樂本從民心而來乃成於樂故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3345:3365'>感動人深也其移風易俗者風謂水土之風氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3365:3392'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-9a' );" name="018-9a" class="pb">[018-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3392:3406'>謂舒疾剛柔俗謂君上之情欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3406:3423'><span class='krp-note'>十/二</span>饗禮依命數春秋有不然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3423:3443'>正義曰凡饗禮案大行人云上公九獻侯伯七</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3443:3463'>獻子男五獻並依命數其臣介則孤同子男郷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3463:3483'>大夫略爲一節俱三獻則天子諸侯之士同壹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3483:3503'>獻故昭六年季孫宿如晉晉侯享之有加籩武</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3503:3523'>子退使行人告曰得貺不過三獻是其事也但</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3523:3543'>春秋亂丗之法或有大夫五獻者故昭元年鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3543:3563'>伯享趙孟具五獻之籩豆於幙下是亂丗之法</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3563:3590'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-9b' );" name="018-9b" class="pb">[018-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3590:3610'>也或者鄭以公孤之禮享趙孟故五獻也言百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3610:3630'>拜喻多者案今郷飲酒之禮是壹獻也無百拜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3630:3640'>今云百拜故喻多也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3640:3660'><span class='krp-note'>十/三</span>君德形於樂音而民之憂樂從之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3660:3680'>夫樂聲善惡本由民心而生所感善事則善聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3680:3701'>應所感惡事則惡聲起樂之善惡𥘉則從民心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3701:3721'>而興後乃合成爲樂樂又下感於人善樂感人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3721:3741'>則人化之爲善惡樂感人則人隨之爲惡是樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3741:3761'>出於人而還感人猶如雨岀於山而還雨山火</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3761:3789'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-10a' );" name="018-10a" class="pb">[018-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3789:3809'>出於木而還燔木故此篇之首論人能興樂此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3809:3829'>章之意論樂能感人也　夫民有血氣心知之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3829:3849'>性者人由血氣而有心知故血氣心知連言之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3849:3869'>其性雖一所感不恒故云而無哀樂喜怒之常</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3869:3889'>也　應感起物而動者言内心應感起於外物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3889:3909'>謂物感己心遂應之念慮興動故云應感起物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3909:3929'>而動　然後心術形焉者術謂所由道路也形</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3929:3949'>見也以其感物所動故然後心之所由道路而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3949:3969'>形見也心術見者即下文是也　是故志微噍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='3969:3997'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-10b' );" name="018-10b" class="pb">[018-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='3997:4017'>殺之音作而民思憂者志微謂人君志意微細</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4017:4037'>噍殺謂樂聲噍蹙殺小如此音作而民感之則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4037:4057'>悲思憂愁也　嘽諧慢易繁文簡節之音作而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4057:4077'>民康樂者嘽寛也諧和也慢䟽也繁多也簡節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4077:4097'>易少也康安也言君若道德嘽和䟽易則樂音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4097:4117'>多文采而節奏簡略則下民所以安樂也　粗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4117:4137'>厲猛起奮末廣賁之音作而民剛毅者粗厲謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4137:4157'>人君性氣粗䟽威厲猛起謂武猛發起奮末謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4157:4177'>奮動手足廣賁謂樂聲廣大憤氣充滿如此音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4177:4205'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-11a' );" name="018-11a" class="pb">[018-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4205:4225'>作而民感之則性氣剛毅也　廉直勁正莊誠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4225:4245'>之音作而民肅敬者君若廉直勁正則樂音矜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4245:4266'>莊嚴栗而誠信故民應之而肅敬也　寛𥙿肉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4266:4286'>好順成和動之音作而民慈愛者肉謂厚重者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4286:4307'>也君上如寛𥙿厚重則樂音順序而和諧動作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4307:4327'>故民皆應之而慈愛也　流辟邪散狄成滌濫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4327:4347'>之音作而民淫亂者流辟謂君志流移不静邪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4347:4367'>散謂違辟不正放邪散亂狄成滌濫皆謂徃來</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4367:4387'>速疾謂樂之曲折速疾而成速疾而止僣濫謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4387:4415'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-11b' );" name="018-11b" class="pb">[018-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4415:4435'>樂聲急速如此音作民感之淫亂也此六事所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4435:4455'>云音者皆據君德及樂音相雜也君德好而樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4455:4475'>音亦好君德惡而樂音亦惡皆上句論君德下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4475:4481'>句論樂音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4481:4501'><span class='krp-note'>十/四</span>樂師宗祝啇祝知末節故位處卑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4501:4521'>樂師辨乎聲詩故北面而弦者此明知禮樂末</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4521:4541'>者其位處卑即樂師以辨曉聲詩但知樂之末</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4541:4561'>節故北面而皷弦言其位處卑也　宗祝辨乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4561:4581'>宗廟之禮故後尸者宗謂宗人祝謂大祝但辨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4581:4609'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-12a' );" name="018-12a" class="pb">[018-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4609:4629'>曉於宗廟詔相之禮故在尸後也　啇祝辨乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4629:4649'>䘮禮故後主人者啇祝謂習啇禮而爲祝者但</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4649:4669'>辨曉死䘮擯相之禮故後主人謂在主人之後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4669:4689'>言此宗祝啇祝但知禮之末節故在尸與主人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4689:4699'>後言其位處卑賤也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4699:4715'><span class='krp-note'>十/五</span>魏文侯畢萬後僣諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4715:4735'>云魏文侯畢萬之後僣諸侯者也者案春秋閔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4735:4755'>元年晉獻公滅魏以魏賜畢萬案丗本云萬生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4755:4775'>芒芒生季季生武仲州州生莊子降降生獻子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4775:4803'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-12b' );" name="018-12b" class="pb">[018-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4803:4823'>荼荼生簡子取取生襄子多多生桓子駒駒生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4823:4834'>文侯斯是畢萬之後也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4834:4854'><span class='krp-note'>十/六</span>新樂之發獶雜如漢人有獼猴舞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4854:4874'>今夫新樂進俯退俯姦聲以濫溺而不止及優</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4874:4894'>侏儒獶雜子女不知父子樂終不可以語不可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4894:4914'>以道古此新樂之發也注云俯猶曲也言不齊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4914:4934'>一也濫濫竊也溺而不止聲淫亂無以治之獶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4934:4954'>獼猴也言舞者如獼猴戲也亂男女之尊卑獶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4954:4974'>或爲優正義曰案詩小雅云母教猱升木毛傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4974:5002'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-13a' );" name="018-13a" class="pb">[018-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5002:5022'>云猱猨屬也是獶獼猴也漢書檀長卿爲獼猴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5022:5030'>舞是狀如獼猴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5030:5042'><span class='krp-note'>十/七</span>樂與音不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5042:5062'>夫樂者與音相近而不同注云言文侯好音而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5062:5080'>不知樂也鏗鎗之類皆爲音應律乃爲樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5080:5097'><span class='krp-note'>十/八</span>鄭宋衛齊溺音祭祀弗用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5097:5117'>子夏對曰鄭音好濫淫志宋音燕女溺志衛音</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5117:5137'>趨數煩志齊音敖辟喬志此四者皆淫於色而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5137:5157'>害於德是以祭祀弗用也注云言四國皆出此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5157:5185'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-13b' );" name="018-13b" class="pb">[018-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5185:5205'>溺音濫濫竊姦聲也燕安也春秋傳曰懷與安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5205:5225'>實敗名趨數讀爲促速聲之誤也煩勞也祭祀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5225:5232'>者不用淫樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5232:5246'><span class='krp-note'>十/九</span>敬以和何事不行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5246:5266'>詩云肅雍和鳴先祖是聽夫肅肅敬也雍雝和</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5266:5286'>也夫敬以和何事不行注云言古樂敬且和故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5286:5298'>無事而不用溺音無所施</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5298:5314'><span class='krp-note'>二/十</span>未及下車與周紀義反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5314:5334'>未及下車者言速封諸侯未遑暇及下車即封</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5334:5362'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-14a' );" name="018-14a" class="pb">[018-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5362:5382'>黃帝堯舜之後下車而封夏殷之後者以二王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5382:5402'>之後以其禮大故待下車而封之案周本紀云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5402:5422'>武王以與戰伐紂兵皆崩畔武王入至紂死之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5422:5442'>所周公把大鉞畢公把小鉞以夾武王武王旣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5442:5462'>入立社南召公奭貢兵師尚父牽牲尹逸祝曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5462:5482'>殷之末孫季紂殄廢先王明德又云乃封紂子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5482:5502'>禄父使其弟管叔蔡叔相禄父命召公釋箕子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5502:5522'>之囚命畢公釋百姓之囚表啇容之閭命南宫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5522:5542'>适散鹿臺之財發鉅橋之粟命閎夭封比于之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5542:5570'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-14b' );" name="018-14b" class="pb">[018-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5570:5590'>墓武王追思先聖乃褒封神農之後於焦及封</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5590:5610'>黃帝之後於薊封帝堯之後於祝封帝舜之後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5610:5630'>於陳大禹與此同然如武王追思先聖乃封之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5630:5650'>與此未及下車義反當以禮記爲正此不云封</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5650:5661'>神農者舉三恪二代也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5661:5676'><span class='krp-note'>卄/一</span>文王之廟如明堂制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5676:5696'>祀乎明堂而民知孝注云文王之廟爲明堂制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5696:5716'>正義曰於時未有明堂而云明堂者文王廟如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5716:5736'>明堂之制周公攝政六年始朝諸侯於明堂當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5736:5764'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-15a' );" name="018-15a" class="pb">[018-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5764:5784'>武王伐紂之時未有明堂今云祀乎明堂故知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5784:5798'>是文王之廟制耳非正明堂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5798:5818'><span class='krp-note'>卄/二</span>油然羙好貌利欲少則情性和樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5818:5838'>致樂以治心則易直子諒之心油然生矣易直</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5838:5858'>子諒之心生則樂樂則安安則乆乆則天天則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5858:5878'>神注云油然新生好貌也善心生則寡於利欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5878:5898'>寡於利欲則樂矣志明行成不言而見信如天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5898:5918'>也不怒而見畏如神也正義曰書傳箕子歌云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5918:5938'>禾黍之油油潤澤好之貌然善心内生其貌美</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='5938:5966'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-15b' );" name="018-15b" class="pb">[018-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='5966:5986'>好油然也云善心生則寡於利欲者凡利欲之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='5986:6006'>發由貪鄙而來心若思利欲則神勞形苦今善</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='6006:6026'>心旣生則貪欲寡少利欲旣少則情性和樂云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6026:6046'>志明行成者不貪不利用是志意清明神和性</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6046:6055'>樂是善行得成矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6055:6074'><span class='krp-note'>廿/三</span>德輝謂顔色理謂容貌之進止</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6074:6094'>故德輝動於内而民莫不承聽理發諸外而民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6094:6114'>莫不承順注云德輝顔色潤澤也理容貌之進</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6114:6134'>止也正義曰德輝顔色潤澤也由内心和順故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6134:6162'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-16a' );" name="018-16a" class="pb">[018-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6162:6182'>和順之德輝然發見於顔色是德輝由動於内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6182:6202'>而來也云理容貌之進止也者以經云理發諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6202:6222'>外凡道理從内心而生今云理發諸外非道理</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='6222:6242'>之理止謂容貌進止之理鄭恐有道理之嫌故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='6242:6251'>云容貌之進止也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='6251:6271'><span class='krp-note'>卄/四</span>邵公蓋黃帝後或謂文王之庶子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='6271:6291'>封黃帝之後於薊音計今涿郡薊縣是即燕國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='6291:6311'>之都也孔安國司馬遷及鄭皆云燕國郡邵公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='6311:6331'>與周同姓案黃帝姓姬君奭盖其後也或黃帝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='6331:6359'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '018-16b' );" name="018-16b" class="pb">[018-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='6359:6379'>之後封薊者滅絶而更封燕郡乎疑不能明也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='6379:6399'>而皇甫謐以邵公爲文王之庶子記傳更無所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='6399:6417'>出又左傳冨辰之言亦無燕也<span class='krp-note'>陸釋</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='6417:6427'>禮記要義卷第十九</span><br/>
